text: Daan Vekemans (born 22 February 2000) is a Belgian professional footballer who plays for OH Leuven in the Belgian First Division B. Vekemans made his debut for OH Leuven on 18 February 2018 in the home match against Beerschot Wilrijk, three days before his 18th birthday. == References == Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Oud-Heverlee Leuven players Category:SC Eendracht Aalst players Category:Belgian Second Division/Belgian First Division B players
